item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Jazz Jackrabbit 1 & 2 Soundtrack
item.description:
This is probably a long shot but for all my gamers here:

Does anybody have the Jazz Jackrabbit 1 & 2 Soundtrack that was released in 2013 as part of the Retro Game Music Bundle? The lossless version was available to buy only for a short time; the only instance of this Soundtrack still being available online is on Spotify, but I don't use streaming and AFAIK Spotify doesn't have Hi-Fi audio.
This is the album, for reference:


Any pointer in the right direction would be helpful, thanks.
